"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-23-people-getting-kit-off-take-part-naked-olympics-21279386\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A group of sport-loving nudists have held their ownOlympics- with all competitors playing in their birthday suits.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From volleyball to boules, the naturists spent the weekend flexing their talents at the Yorkshire Sun Society in Hull from July 19 to 21.\", \"from\": 116, \"to\": 253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The event was organised by British Naturism, who were getting into the spirit of sport with the 2024ParisOlympics set to begin later this week.\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 282, \"end\": 298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Naturism\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Naturism\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Naturism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Naturism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Naturists would argue their weekend was closer to the ancient Olympics inGreece, where competitors took part naked.\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 515, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tickets to the event cost up to \\u00a370, which included a camping spot with an electrical hook-up.\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Start your day informed with Metro'sNews Updatesnewsletter or getBreaking Newsalerts the moment it happens.\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 720, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The venue also featured an indoor pool, hot tub and sauna for the athletes to relax in after a long day competing.\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 836, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 26-acre woodland-based club also offered nude walks around the grounds, if that tickles your fancy.\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"British Naturism advertised the event and said: 'The weekend is fun and you are free to enjoy the sporting events or just chill out as you wish.\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Naturism\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Naturism\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Naturism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Naturism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We have the following sports available: Miniten, Boules, Pool Volleyball, 8-ball Pool and indoor games, all equipment will be available and the members will teach you how to play those games you have not tried before.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1139, \"end\": 1145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boules\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Boules\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boules\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boules\"}, {\"begin\": 1152, \"end\": 1162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volleyball\", \"score\": 0.9999999998185558, \"rank\": 1.8132495945239167e-10, \"text\": \"Volleyball\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volleyball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volleyball\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The club has a wonderfully maintained indoor pool, Hot Tub and Sauna for your use through the weekend.\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1412, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Other facilities are; a centrally heated clubhouse with a licensed bar and a large kitchen used by members and visitors for self-catering.\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Other facilities include TV, Wi-Fi, Library, etc.\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1605, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As well as the usual toilets and showers.\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The club is located in 26 acres of beautiful woodland with several walks available, backtrack, the meadows and the river walk.'\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1777, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2016 at the Rio Olympic Games, nudists heldnaked games on the beachin a tribute to the original way of doing Olympic Sports.\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1906, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Get in touch with our news team by emailing us atwebnews@metro.co.uk.\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1965, \"end\": 1976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_(British_newspaper)\", \"score\": 0.9993608704165835, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"metro.co.uk\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_(British_newspaper)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_(British_newspaper)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our news page.\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 2026, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Snoop Dogg proudly carries Olympic 2024 torch through Paris becoming unlikely star  ArrowMORE:Team GB swimmer Ben Proud aiming to make it third-time lucky at Paris Olympics  ArrowMORE:Why the Paris Olympics has ditched McDonald's and what athletes will be eating instead  Stay on top of the headlines with daily email updates.\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2364, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2092, \"end\": 2097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999770353, \"rank\": 2.3001007029137105e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2148, \"end\": 2157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Proud\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ben Proud\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Proud\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Proud\"}, {\"begin\": 2230, \"en